c ---------------------Input of Special Symbols-------------------------------------------------
c 
c The input section here is for rules that must precede other rules
c 
  + '_' > U+135F c gemination
  U+135F + '_' > '_'

c The following two rules had to be added here (not later) to fix the deadkey issue
